{"tid":1556267,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國下議院議長白高漢 (John Bercow) 請辭，十月底脫歐日下台","createTime":"2019-09-09T16:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T08:59:31.000Z","uid":35221,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a3ba96aa2ef352233286d0df85f9782ded5025d7","tid":1556267,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:06:36.000Z","msg":"英國下議院議長貝爾考(白高漢)請辭 十月底脫歐日下台<br />\n2019-09-09 23:29<br />\n聯合報 記者羅方妤╱即時報導<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/09/09/realtime/6800529.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F09%2F09%2Frealtime%2F6800529.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=a31901b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國下議院議長貝爾考(白高漢)9日宣布請辭。（美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n繼英國就業及退休保障大臣魯德(盧綺婷 Amber Rudd)7日請辭後，保守黨籍下議院議長貝爾考(白高漢)9日宣布請辭。CNN報導，貝爾考(白高漢)表示，若首相強生(莊漢生 Boris Johnson)9日稍晚能讓國會同意提前舉行大選，他會馬上離職。<br />\n<br />\n一般預料，提前大選案難以在國會過關。貝爾考(白高漢)說，如果是這樣，他會在10月31日英國預定的脫歐日下台。<br />\n<br />\n貝爾考(白高漢)告訴國會議員：「如果不提前大選，我認為最不具破壞性且最民主的方式就是，我在10月31日當天工作時間結束時下台。」<br />\n<br />\n首相強生(莊漢生)已奏請女王並獲批准，英國國會將在9日議程結束後休會，10月14日才開議。強生(莊漢生)在英國即將脫歐之際採取這項作法，被反對者批評是蓄意關閉國會，讓國會無法阻止他在10月底無協議脫歐。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/tJMVcTfzDdL1pOGxlk/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FtJMVcTfzDdL1pOGxlk%2Fgiphy.gif&h=0ce8b28c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6809/4038574\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6809%2F4038574&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNpszS%2Fgy1fqSqMk7TcT3QhU%3D&h=120c0c55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6809/4038574</a>"},{"pid":"fa665c5337b697a77927cb895c64782391995a84","tid":1556267,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T18:15:07.000Z","msg":"乘亂 又財技搵銀~<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb7811c555998af987a2dabbcfe8e1e1e23f6a54","tid":1556267,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa665c5337b697a77927cb895c64782391995a84","tid":1556267,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T18:15:07.000Z","msg":"乘亂 又財技搵銀~<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:55:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42f472600d5e308bd67359d655fc5a03332a8a56","tid":1556267,"uid":284592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:59:31.000Z","msg":"ORDER! ORDER! OOOORDEEEEER!"}]}